text: Cornelia Lister and Nina Stojanović were the defending champions, but both players chose not to participate. Nicoleta Dascălu and Raluca Șerban won the title, defeating Lucie Hradecká and Johana Marková in the final, 6–4, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Advantage Cars Prague Open - Doubles Category:Advantage Cars Prague Open
